relevant_findings.HEENT: Normocephalic, atraumatic, pupils equal, round, reactive to light, oral pharynx clear, dry mucous membranes
relevant_findings.cardiovascular: Regular rate and rhythm, normal S1 and S2, no murmurs, rubs, or gallops
relevant_findings.lungs: Clear to auscultation bilaterally, no wheezing, rales, or rhonchi
relevant_findings.abdomen: Soft, non-tender, non-distended, no flank dullness
relevant_findings.extremities: Warm, well perfused, no cyanosis, edema, or erythema
